{"tid":1638458,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急幫幫手去表揚新港城中心保安員","createTime":"2019-10-08T10:16:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T10:54:57.000Z","uid":41366,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fc5bb08a1b3201ec022fd274d4073215ea67cee7","tid":1638458,"uid":41366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:16:39.000Z","msg":"各位朋友，你地可唔可以幫幫手<br />\n昨晚阻止警察入馬鞍山新港城中心的secu面臨被炒，宜家還有大量藍絲一式一樣的電郵話保安人員阻差辦公&hellip;<br />\n大家請幫忙電郵去呢度，表揚保安人員英勇專業，保障客人利益？<br />\n<br />\n表揚新港城中心保安員<br />\nEmail to: corpcomm@hld.com, portfolio.leasing@hld.com, Henderson@hld.com<br />\n<br />\n致新港城中心保安公司︰<br />\n<br />\n你好，本人在網上媒體中看到在2019年10月7日晚上，有幾位保安員落力阻止警察在沒有法庭搜查令的情況下進入新港城中心，他們數人螳臂擋車，雖然最後未能阻止警察胡亂闖入商場，但他們盡心盡力，英勇專業，保障客人利益，行為值得表揚，敬請貴管理公司能珍惜此等員工。謝謝﹗<br />\n<br />\n普通市民XXX"},{"pid":"281cb2c65222765a0e6afe485cd1527909bb2fc8","tid":1638458,"uid":121153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:48:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da39b353b88ec17b60a39d37f4f9bee072d3f40f","tid":1638458,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:50:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd28052bc20e660d212ba16f0a04cca66f59c5ba","tid":1638458,"uid":41366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"281cb2c65222765a0e6afe485cd1527909bb2fc8","tid":1638458,"uid":121153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:48:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:07:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e5d84b50b4e5649794ae841c66b53b0b6b0cf2","tid":1638458,"uid":210155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:36:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8d2abdd8ffa4e8ea5ae5b9a847181b1837e7c091","tid":1638458,"uid":154034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:04:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6426d82133f83b6dca75655da9d6442b0963a7f0","tid":1638458,"uid":12824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:04:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fede0132a47dfc7e570af7342f59277f537a768","tid":1638458,"uid":41366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:21:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e55f94e8c46aed504d07e6e53528ba9fb1b358b9","tid":1638458,"uid":265935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:28:17.000Z","msg":"主題：<br />\n表揚新港城中心5名保安員及解僱謠傳<br />\n<br />\n內容：<br />\n<br />\n致恆基兆業地產有限公司及冠威管理有限公司︰<br />\n<br />\n本人得悉於2019年10月7日晚上，有約5名新港城中心的保安員，因警方沒有法庭搜查令的情況下欲違法進入商場及闖入私人物業，該5名保安員只是盡力阻止無理要求。本人知悉該5名新港城中心保安因涉阻差辦公被捕。他們盡心盡力，英勇專業地保障街坊及顧客的安全，他們英勇盡責的行為值得表揚，特函讚揚該數名保安員。<br />\n<br />\n網傳恆基兆業地產即將因警方要求解僱該5名新港城中心保安，但本人認為恆地一直以港為家，維護港人利益，對於有關解僱謠傳非常懷疑，煩請釐清。<br />\n<br />\n此致"},{"pid":"dd92ac531f3c0018420be06268d52461d3d306b1","tid":1638458,"uid":41366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:51:16.000Z","msg":"大家sd左 email未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea5cff575cfd9bf5e67746863cb4a612844c727b","tid":1638458,"uid":101483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:54:57.000Z","msg":"推"}]}